The paper discusses challenges in performing online analytics for IoT and CPS applications, which are typically related to data management and processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Databases), which deals with data storage, retrieval, and management. The paper also discusses real-time computing and fault recovery, which are related to distributed systems and software engineering, respectively. Therefore, cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.SY (Systems and Control) are also likely categories. Finally, the paper mentions Smart Grid as a case study, which is related to cyber-physical systems and control. Therefore, cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also a possible category.
